      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the heads up about the cipro. i'll avoid that. but you mentioned pseudoephedrine... i saw a bottle of Sudafed in my cabinet from before i got pregnant. is that one actually safe or is it just like \"generally\" okay? i'm pretty desperate to breathe through my nose again.",
