      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I would advise against taking a double dose of Sudafed, even if you're desperate for sleep. While it's usually safe to take the recommended dose, taking a double dose can increase the risk of side effects like dizziness, anxiety, and insomnia. If you need to take a larger dose, I'd recommend consulting your doctor or taking a smaller dose every 4-6 hours, rather than a large dose all at once.",
